        "observed_type": "title",
        "canon_role": "section_header",
        "text": "年报解读：线上和线下渠道协同发力构建银行渠道 新生态式服务体系",
        "bbox": [
          0.054816606207174524,
          0.4178423827846658,
          0.4095122934300685,
          0.4480547242411287
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_yanbaor2_8072f7ea9b3083ff5e8f9bfbba591771e61115039c96fda1c8ea391a7570f098.pdf_13_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "我们注意到越来越多的银正在呈现“以用户为中 ”、“客户上”的经营理念，那什么才是银 获取用户、触达用户、经营用户、维系用户最重要 的前沿阵地呢?",
        "bbox": [
          0.054816606207174524,
          0.450334900954824,
          0.4095122934300685,
          0.5130397605814451
        ],
        "order": 5
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "eu_id": "EU-0004",
    "kind": "section_text_panel",
    "page": "yanbaor2_8072f7ea9b3083ff5e8f9bfbba591771e61115039c96fda1c8ea391a7570f098.pdf_13",
